rows.label: tlk41100124_04_msg0001
rows.name:
Have you visited the weird house just
below here? There's a game called
TIGER! TIGER! right by the entrance.

rows.label: tlk41100124_04_msg0002
rows.name:
I tried playing it on a whim, and it was
incredibly addictive. I was hooked for hours!

rows.label: tlk41100124_04_msg0003
rows.name:
My high score right now is
18,310 points!

rows.label: tlk41100124_04_msg0004
rows.name:
I wanted to become a botanist,
but maybe I should aim to become a
pro TIGER! TIGER! player instead...
